  <entry>
    <title>Typora常用语法大全</title>
    <url>/2025/07/12/Typora%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A8/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、标题（Markdown">一、标题（Markdown)</h2>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="二、字体样式（Markdown）">二、字体样式（Markdown）</h2>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**加粗**</span> 或 <span class="strong">__加粗__</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span> 或 <span class="emphasis">_斜体_</span></span><br><span class="line">~~删除线~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">`行内代码`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="三、列表（Markdown）">三、列表（Markdown）</h2>
<h3 id="无序列表">无序列表</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 项目1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 项目2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  -</span> 子项目</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="有序列表">有序列表</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 项目1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 项目2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="四、引用-分割线（Markdown）">四、引用 &amp; 分割线（Markdown）</h2>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 这是一个引用内容</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是分割线</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="五、代码块（Markdown）">五、代码块（Markdown）</h2>
<h3 id="行内代码">行内代码</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`代码内容`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="多行代码">多行代码</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">```语言</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">代码内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="例如：">例如：</h4>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">```python</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">print(&quot;Hello World&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="六、表格（Markdown）">六、表格（Markdown）</h2>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 姓名 | 年龄 | 性别 |</span><br><span class="line">| ---- | ---- | ---- |</span><br><span class="line">| 张三 | 18   | 男   |</span><br><span class="line">| 李四 | 20   | 女   |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="七、插入图片和链接（Markdown）">七、插入图片和链接（Markdown）</h2>
<h3 id="图片：">图片：</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片描述</span>](<span class="link">图片地址</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="链接：">链接：</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">链接文字</span>](<span class="link">链接地址</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="八、任务列表（Markdown）">八、任务列表（Markdown）</h2>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [ ] 任务一</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [x] 已完成任务</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="九、HTML-拓展语法（Typora支持）">九、HTML 拓展语法（Typora支持）</h2>
<h3 id="居中对齐：">居中对齐：</h3>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span>要居中的内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="或者用-CSS：">或者用 CSS：</h4>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text-align:center;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>居中文本<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="修改字体颜色：">修改字体颜色：</h3>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;color:red;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>红色字体<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="修改字体大小：">修改字体大小：</h3>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;font-size:20px;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>大号字体<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="修改字体样式：">修改字体样式：</h3>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;font-family:楷体;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>楷体字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="插入按钮风格链接：">插入按钮风格链接：</h3>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://example.com&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;padding: 6px 12px; background-color: pink; color: white; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>点击这里<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="居中插入图片（适合图床）">居中插入图片（适合图床）</h3>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span> <span class="attr">align</span>=<span class="string">&quot;center&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;图片地址&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;300&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="多列排版：">多列排版：</h3>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;display: flex; justify-content: space-between;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;width: 48%;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>左边内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;width: 48%;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>右边内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="十、数学公式（LaTeX）">十、数学公式（LaTeX）</h2>
<h3 id="行内公式：">行内公式：</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个公式：$E = mc^2$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="块级公式：">块级公式：</h3>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\sum<span class="emphasis">_&#123;i=1&#125;^&#123;n&#125; i = \frac&#123;n(n+1)&#125;&#123;2&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">$$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="十一、目录（TOC）">十一、目录（TOC）</h2>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[TOC]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>自动生成目录（需要开启支持）</p>
<h2 id="十二、摘要分隔符">十二、摘要分隔符</h2>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
