  <entry>
    <title>恢复博客过程的存档</title>
    <url>/2025/07/10/%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%98%E6%A1%A3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言">前言</h2>
<p>重新搭建博客的过程，算不上顺利，hexo的配置、主题、插件等等都需要一点点摸索，过程中踩了不少坑，也有很多收获。</p>
<p>主要是我对编程真的一窍不通，但是我又爱折腾，感觉拥有一个自己的网站这件事还是蛮酷的。<br>
感谢那些帮助过我的人，感谢那些开源项目，感谢开源社区的贡献者。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<p>这个过程中我遇到了很多问题，几乎所有问题都是通过Chatgpt完成的，但首先，我要感谢的不是Chatgpt，而是 <a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git</a> 这个项目的作者，他的项目帮助我解决了很多问题，让我学到了很多。我的主题就是用的这个的Gemmini主题，配置很全面，自定义程度也高，为我这个小白解决了许多问题。此外。感谢 <a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo.git">https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo.git</a> 这个项目的作者，这个项目可以把图片上传到Github的个人图床，我用这个上传了我的博客的图片，方便管理。最后才是感谢GPT，很多问题找不到答案的时候，GPT可以给我指导。</p>
<p>下面是我整理的重新部署博客的整个过程：</p>
<h2 id="新建一个Hexo源码项目">新建一个Hexo源码项目</h2>
<p>重新部署博客文件后GitHub上的项目就会被新的覆盖掉，以前的博客内容就全都没了，所以如果你以前的博客有重要内容，建议先把旧的博客克隆到本地再重新部署。</p>
<p>克隆你的仓库到本地</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/你的用户名/你的仓库名.git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> 你的仓库名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>新建一个本地 Hexo 博客源码目录：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init hexo-blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> hexo-blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>配置部署信息（<code>_config.yml</code> 末尾添加）：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/hespring/hespring.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>安装部署插件：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>PS：如果想要修改<code>hexo-blog</code>文件的位置，可以直接移动<code>hexo-blog</code>文件，然后放到想要的位置就可以了。</p>
<h2 id="写一篇文章">写一篇文章</h2>
<p>博主部署的时候用的是VS Code写的，调试主题配置比较方便。</p>
<p>在你当前的目录文件夹<code>hexo-blog/</code>中右键，选择<code>Open Git Bash here</code>运行：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new post <span class="string">&quot;我的第一篇 Hexo 博客&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这个文件会生成在<code>hexo-blog\source\_posts</code>目录下，文件名字就是<code>我的第一篇-Hexo-博客.md</code></p>
<p>用VS Code打开<code>我的第一篇-Hexo-博客.md</code>文件，可以写一些内容，比如;</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 我的第一篇 Hexo 博客</span><br><span class="line">date: 2025-07-09 23:00:00</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> Hexo</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 博客</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">- 随笔</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">欢迎来到我的博客！这是我用 Hexo 写的第一篇文章。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><code>ctrl+s</code>保存之后就可以使用Hexo一键三连了<code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code>,然后打开浏览器访问：<a href="http://localhost:4000">http://localhost:4000</a> 就可看到文章了。</p>
<h2 id="NEXT主题">NEXT主题</h2>
<p>仓库地址：<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git</a></p>
<p>在博客的根目录下选择<code>themes</code>文件夹右键选择<code>Open Git Bash here</code>运行以下内容：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> hexo</span><br><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>打开路径<code>hexo-blog\themes\next</code>先修改配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，选择用VS Code打开;</p>
<p>在这一块修改浏览器标签页左侧的小图标<code>favicon</code>，推荐在这个网站生成  <a href="https://realfavicongenerator.net/">https://realfavicongenerator.net/</a> 选择自己喜欢的图片就可以生成全部需要的图标了。把下面的图片1、图片2等都替换成自己的图片名称。</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">favicon:</span>        <span class="comment"># 网站图标路径，默认路径为：hexo-blog\themes\next\source\images</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">small:</span> <span class="string">/images/图片1.png</span>      <span class="comment"># 小图标路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">medium:</span> <span class="string">/images/图片2.png</span>   <span class="comment"># 中图标路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">apple_touch_icon:</span> <span class="string">/图片3.png</span>  <span class="comment"># 苹果设备图标路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">safari_pinned_tab:</span> <span class="string">/images/favicon.svg</span>      <span class="comment"># Safari 标签图标路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#android_manifest: /images/manifest.json     # Android 应用清单路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#ms_browserconfig: /images/browserconfig.xml       # Windows 8 应用清单路径</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这个主题有四种方案，分别是Muse|Mist|Pisces|Gemini，默认是Muse，可以根据自己的喜好在配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>中的这个部分修改，把前面的#去掉就是启用，加上#就是不启用。</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Schemes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Muse           # 网站配色方案，默认 Muse</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Mist</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Pisces</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">scheme:</span> <span class="string">Gemini</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>接下来是菜单设置部分，可以根据自己的需求修改，比如我把关于、归档、分类、标签这四个菜单都打开，其他的都关掉。</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span>                     <span class="comment"># 菜单设置</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span>      <span class="comment"># 主页</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">about:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-user</span>      <span class="comment"># 关于</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span>        <span class="comment"># 标签</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-th</span>      <span class="comment"># 分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive    # 归档</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar      # 时间线</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap      # 站点地图</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat        # 公益捐助</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#search: /search/ || fa fa-search      # 搜索</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">photos:</span> <span class="string">/photos/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-camera</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#games: /games/ || fa fa-gamepad</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>​	这样显示的是英文，我想要的是中文，所以我是这么写的：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span>                     <span class="comment"># 菜单设置</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">首页:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span>      <span class="comment"># 主页</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">关于:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-user</span>      <span class="comment"># 关于</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span>        <span class="comment"># 标签</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-th</span>      <span class="comment"># 分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive    # 归档</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar      # 时间线</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap      # 站点地图</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat        # 公益捐助</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#搜索: /search/ || fa fa-search      # 搜索</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">相册:</span> <span class="string">/photos/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-camera</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#游戏: /games/ || fa fa-gamepad</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这样就能看到中文了。需要注意的是关于、标签、分类、相册这四个功能需要额外配置，具体操作如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page about</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page photos</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>hexo-blog\source目录下会生成about、tags、categories、photos四个文件夹，里面分别是对应的index.md文件，修改里面的内容即可，比如about页面：</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 关于</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">date: 2025-07-10</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">你好！我是 <span class="strong">*** ，这是我的个人博客，用于分享技术、生活和学习笔记。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">欢迎来到我的博客，这里有我的一些文章和笔记，欢迎与我交流。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">tags页面：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">title: 标签</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">date: 2025-07-10 22:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">layout: &quot;tags&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">categories页面：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">title: 分类</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">type: categories</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">由于NEXT主题没有自带的相册功能，所以这个相册功能是我让GPT写的一个相册页面，我的图片来源是在GitHub上，所以我用PicGo上传图片到GitHub图床，然后在相册页面引用图片，具体方法会在另一篇文章中说明，这里只是实现相册功能。具体代码如下：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">```markdown</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">title: 我的相册</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">layout: page</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">date: 2025-07-10 22:30:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">&lt;!-- ✅ 标题说明 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;margin-bottom: 10px; color: #888; font-size: 16px;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">  这里是我的个人相册，支持分类浏览与关键词搜索。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">&lt;!-- ✅ 统计信息 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;color: #aaa; font-size: 14px;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">  最后更新于：<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;update-time&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">  // 从 meta 标签中读取更新时间（Hexo 会自动插入）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">  const meta = document.querySelector(&#x27;meta[property=&quot;article:modified<span class="emphasis">_time&quot;]&#x27;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  if (meta) &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    const updated = new Date(meta.content);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    const formatted = `$&#123;updated.getFullYear()&#125;-$&#123;(updated.getMonth() + 1).toString().padStart(2, &#x27;0&#x27;)&#125;-$&#123;updated.getDate().toString().padStart(2, &#x27;0&#x27;)&#125;`;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    document.getElementById(&#x27;update-time&#x27;).innerText = formatted;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125; else &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    document.getElementById(&#x27;update-time&#x27;).innerText = &#x27;未知&#x27;;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">&lt;!-- ✅ 分类筛选 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;categoryFilter&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;margin-bottom: 20px;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;category-btn&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-category</span>=<span class="string">&quot;all&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>全部<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;category-btn&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-category</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Galgame&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>Galgame<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;category-btn&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-category</span>=<span class="string">&quot;插图&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>插图<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">&lt;!-- ✅ 搜索框，带放大镜图标 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;position: relative; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto 20px auto;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;searchInput&quot;</span> <span class="attr">placeholder</span>=<span class="string">&quot;搜索照片名...&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;padding: 8px 8px 8px 32px; width: 100%; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fa fa-search&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: #999;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">&lt;!--  如何添加更多图片？复制这段结构一份，修改 data-name 和 data-category 即可。</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;photo&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;图片名称&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-category</span>=<span class="string">&quot;分类名&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;你的图床图片地址&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;图片名称&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span> --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">&lt;!-- ✅ 相册区 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;gallery&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;photo&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;新堂彩音1&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-category</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Galgame&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://github.com/HeSpring/picgo/blob/main/%E6%96%B0%E5%A0%82%E5%BD%A9%E9%9F%B31.png?raw=true&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;新堂彩音1&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;photo&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;风又音理&quot;</span> <span class="attr">data-category</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Galgame&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://github.com/HeSpring/picgo/blob/main/2023-11-15_183419.png?raw=true&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;风又音理&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  <span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &lt;!-- 更多图片复制这个结构，修改 data-name 和 data-category --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">&lt;!-- ✅ 搜索 + 分类脚本 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  const input = document.getElementById(&#x27;searchInput&#x27;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  const photos = document.querySelectorAll(&#x27;#gallery .photo&#x27;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  const categoryButtons = document.querySelectorAll(&#x27;.category-btn&#x27;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  let currentCategory = &#x27;all&#x27;;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  input.addEventListener(&#x27;input&#x27;, filterPhotos);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  categoryButtons.forEach(btn =&gt; &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    btn.addEventListener(&#x27;click&#x27;, function () &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      currentCategory = this.getAttribute(&#x27;data-category&#x27;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      categoryButtons.forEach(b =&gt; b.classList.remove(&#x27;active&#x27;));</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      this.classList.add(&#x27;active&#x27;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      filterPhotos();</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    &#125;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  function filterPhotos() &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    const keyword = input.value.toLowerCase();</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    photos.forEach(photo =&gt; &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      const name = photo.getAttribute(&#x27;data-name&#x27;).toLowerCase();</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      const category = photo.getAttribute(&#x27;data-category&#x27;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      const matchKeyword = name.includes(keyword);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      const matchCategory = (currentCategory === &#x27;all&#x27; || currentCategory === category);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">      photo.style.display = matchKeyword &amp;&amp; matchCategory ? &#x27;&#x27; : &#x27;none&#x27;;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    &#125;);</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">&lt;!-- ✅ 样式美化 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  #gallery &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    display: flex;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    flex-wrap: wrap;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    gap: 16px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    margin-top: 10px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  .photo &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    width: 200px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    text-align: center;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  .photo img &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    max-width: 100%;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    border-radius: 8px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  .caption &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    margin-top: 6px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    font-size: 14px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    color: #555;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  .category-btn &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    padding: 6px 12px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    margin-right: 8px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    background-color: #f2f2f2;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    border: 1px solid #ccc;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    border-radius: 4px;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    cursor: pointer;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  .category-btn.active &#123;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    background-color: #4285f4;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    color: white;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">    border-color: #4285f4;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">  &#125;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这样就能看到相册页面了，可以添加更多照片，并且可以根据分类、关键词搜索。</p>
<h2 id="侧边栏头像自定义">侧边栏头像自定义</h2>
<p>在NEXT的配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>中，可以设置侧边栏头像，具体代码是这一段：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Sidebar Avatar</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span>                   <span class="comment"># 侧边栏头像设置</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Replace the default image and set the url here.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">/images/头像图片名称.png</span>      <span class="comment"># 头像图片路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If true, the avatar will be dispalyed in circle.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rounded:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>           <span class="comment"># 是否显示圆形头像，false表示显示矩形头像，true表示显示圆形头像</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If true, the avatar will be rotated with the cursor.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rotated:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>           <span class="comment"># 是否显示头像旋转动画，false表示不显示，true表示显示</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>把头像图片放到这个路径下即可<code>hexo-blog\themes\next\source\images</code></p>
<p>目前博主就设置了这些，其他配置都没动，主要是看不懂怎么用，所以就先这样了。</p>
<p>最后，别忘了到博客的根目录下的配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>中修改theme为next，然后修改网站的标题、副标题、描述、关键字等信息，然后再<code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code>一键三连，就可以看到自己的博客了。</p>
